### ✅ Create therapist (manual)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/therapists
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Dr. Sanju",
  "email": "drsanju@example.com",
  "phone": "9876543211",
  "languages": ["Hindi", "English"],
  "specializations": ["Anxiety", "Depression"],
  "experienceYears": 5
}

### ✅ Get all therapists
GET http://localhost:3000/api/therapists

### ✅ Get therapist by ID
GET http://localhost:3000/api/therapists/665defabcdefabcdefabcdef

### ✅ Update therapist (requires auth)
PUT http://localhost:3000/api/therapists/665defabcdefabcdefabcdef
Authorization: Bearer <PASTE_JWT_HERE>
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "experienceYears": 8
}